diamonds2 <- diamonds %>% 
  filter(carat <= 2.5) %>% 
  mutate(lprice = log2(price), lcarat = log2(carat))
ggplot(diamonds2, aes(lcarat, lprice)) + 
  geom_hex(bins = 50)
